node.text: Enter this week’s contest right here on Instagram by submitting your caption in the comments below, with the hashtag #MyNewYorkerCaption. Finalists for this week’s cartoon, by Michael Maslin, will appear online July 26th and in the August 2, 2021, issue of the magazine. You must be over 13 to officially enter. Only one submission with the hashtag per username is permitted. Tap the link in our bio for the full contest rules.
